# /pm-do — Execute Task

1. Call `pm_get(task_id)` to read the task details
2. Call `pm_update(task_id, status="in-progress")` to mark it active
3. Read the implementation section and DoD
4. Implement the work described in the task:
   - Follow the implementation instructions
   - Write/modify the specified files
   - Run tests as described
5. Verify all DoD criteria are met
6. Call `pm_update(task_id, status="done")` when complete
7. Summarize what was done
